%TAG !u! tag:unity3d.com,2011:
--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 5e28c2e20bb6c4240a55d8edffb777ec, type: 3}
  m_Name: ChimeFinalNegative
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::NewDialogueData
  npcName: Echo
  dialogueLines:
  - LineID: Start
    Speaker: Chime
    text: Echo!
    lineTone: 0
    NPCGender: female
    NextLineID: II
    endDialogueAfterLine: 0
    choices: []
    objectivesToActivate: []
  - LineID: II
    Speaker: Echo
    text: ...Chime.
    lineTone: 2
    NPCGender: female
    NextLineID: III
    endDialogueAfterLine: 0
    choices: []
    objectivesToActivate: []
  - LineID: III
    Speaker: Chime
    text: Are you okay?! You were corrupted, I had to fight this awful version of
      you.
    lineTone: 0
    NPCGender: female
    NextLineID: IV
    endDialogueAfterLine: 0
    choices: []
    objectivesToActivate: []
  - LineID: IV
    Speaker: Echo
    text: Everything came back to me. This pendant, you gave it to me. It's the reason
      I'm here, right?
    lineTone: 0
    NPCGender: female
    NextLineID: V
    endDialogueAfterLine: 0
    choices: []
    objectivesToActivate: []
  - LineID: V
    Speaker: Chime
    text: ...It's one of the reasons, yes. I'm so sorry, Echo. I didn't want you
      to find out this way.
    lineTone: 0
    NPCGender: female
    NextLineID: VI
    endDialogueAfterLine: 0
    choices: []
    objectivesToActivate: []
  - LineID: VI
    Speaker: Echo
    text: You should be. All this time, I thought you were here to help me. Should've
      known it was too good to be true.
    lineTone: 2
    NPCGender: female
    NextLineID: VII
    endDialogueAfterLine: 0
    choices: []
    objectivesToActivate: []
  - LineID: VIII
    Speaker: Chime
    text: Don't say that! How could say such an awful thing, Echo?
    lineTone: 2
    NPCGender: female
    NextLineID: IX
    endDialogueAfterLine: 0
    choices: []
    objectivesToActivate: []
  - LineID: IX
    Speaker: Echo
    text: Am I wrong? Tell me I'm wrong, Chime.
    lineTone: 0
    NPCGender: female
    NextLineID: X
    endDialogueAfterLine: 0
    choices: []
    objectivesToActivate: []
  - LineID: X
    Speaker: Chime
    text: ...I did believe that the spiritual energy in the pendant I gave you could
      potentially bring you here, but getting my body back was never my only motive!
    lineTone: 0
    NPCGender: female
    NextLineID: XI
    endDialogueAfterLine: 0
    choices: []
    objectivesToActivate: []
  - LineID: XI
    Speaker: Echo
    text: You kept who you really were hidden from me this whole time. I didn't choose
      to forget you, to wipe away the tears, the mourning. It must've been the effects
      of the pendant, of your meddling.
    lineTone: 2
    NPCGender: female
    NextLineID: XII
    endDialogueAfterLine: 0
    choices: []
    objectivesToActivate: []
  - LineID: XII
    Speaker: Chime
    text: You had forgotten all about me, my death, our time together...I wanted
      you to remember, to make you see!
    lineTone: 2
    NPCGender: female
    NextLineID: XIV
    endDialogueAfterLine: 0
    choices: []
    objectivesToActivate: []
  - LineID: XIII
    Speaker: Echo
    text: Oh, I see. I see perfectly clear.
    lineTone: 2
    NPCGender: female
    NextLineID: XIV
    endDialogueAfterLine: 0
    choices: []
    objectivesToActivate: []
  - LineID: XIV
    Speaker: Echo
    text: You used me to set in motion the events that would give you a greater form.
      I'm done being your fool, Chime. I think I'll stay here with my new friends,
      and destroy all of your hard work.
    lineTone: 2
    NPCGender: female
    NextLineID: XV
    endDialogueAfterLine: 0
    choices: []
    objectivesToActivate: []
  - LineID: XIV
    Speaker: Chime
    text: If you mean back to the original world, the one before the Astral Plane,
      I'm afraid we can't...
    lineTone: 0
    NPCGender: female
    NextLineID: XV
    endDialogueAfterLine: 0
    choices: []
    objectivesToActivate: []
  - LineID: XV
    Speaker: Chime
    text: Echo...I can't believe you. You're terrible. You're not the Echo I remembered,
      the one I thought I was bringing here. Something must've changed you.
    lineTone: 2
    NPCGender: female
    NextLineID: XVI
    endDialogueAfterLine: 0
    choices: []
    objectivesToActivate: []
  - LineID: VII
    Speaker: Echo
    text: You needed me as a medium to regain some semblance of form, to get your
      body back. That was your plan all along.
    lineTone: 2
    NPCGender: female
    NextLineID: 
    endDialogueAfterLine: 0
    choices: []
    objectivesToActivate: []
  - LineID: XVI
    Speaker: Chime
    text: I sought to embrace you again, to move on to the next place with you. If
      you don't trust me, there's nothing I can do. Goodbye, Echo...
    lineTone: 0
    NPCGender: female
    NextLineID: 
    endDialogueAfterLine: 1
    choices: []
    objectivesToActivate: []
